18. Important constraints

- Do not execute arbitrary user-provided code.
- Do not upload data anywhere.
- Keep all processing local.
- Do not assume real patient data.
- Do not claim regulatory or clinical validation.
- Do not require a GPU.
- Do not require external APIs.
- Do not block MVP on CLIP, FAISS, MONAI, or heavy models.
- Keep the system usable with simple OpenCV/Pandas/scikit-learn methods.
- Prefer robust engineering and explainable checks over complex ML.

